                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Toss 'N' Turn Spear"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Summons 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Yuegui: Throwing Mode</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/35428890/c587e90a155d07517365218aff66911c_7973158906297745395.png",
                "id": "talent90595",
                "key": "Raphanus Sky Cluster",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Raphanus Sky Cluster"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, creates <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Adeptal Legacy</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Adeptal Legacy</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">After you switch characters:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, heal your active character for 1 HP.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 3</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/35428890/37972e3c3e9c9134cd6b1357f57aa711_246049162204589291.png",
                "id": "talent82350",
                "key": "Moonjade Descent",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 4,
                    "point_type": "dendro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Moonjade Descent"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Summon</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">End Phase:</span> Deal 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro DMG</span>, heal the character on your team that has taken the most damage for 1 HP.<br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/35428890/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6999943259730821948.png",
                "id": "talent65865",
                "key": "Yuegui: Throwing Mode",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/26/35428890/0f3a979856a1d439f1f85900b98bf648_3679804531841794572.png",
                "title": "Yuegui: Throwing Mode"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Dendro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that greants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Burning Flame</span>] that will deal 1 Pyro DMG at the end of the Round (Takes effect once, max 2 stacks)</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] that grants +1 DMG to the next 2 instances of Dendro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/35428890/e8cff941b5a0ff248efde360ec9e91fe_5971069521660579562.png",
                "id": "talent9580",
                "key": "Dendro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Dendro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/09/25/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_1048052833143076108.png",
